<li><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><cite id="CITEREFKimball1856" class="citation cs2">Kimball, Heber C. (December 21, 1856), <a class="external text" href="https://en.wikisource.org/wiki/Journal_of_Discourses/Volume_4/Reformation%E2%80%94A_Test_at_Hand_to_Prove_the_Saints?oldid=462005">"Reformation—A Test at Hand to Prove the Saints"</a>, in Watt, G. D. (ed.), <i>Journal of Discourses Delivered by President Brigham Young, His Two Counsellors, and the Twelve Apostles, and Others</i>, vol.&#160;4, Liverpool: S.W. Richards, pp.&#160;138–45</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.atitle=Reformation%E2%80%94A+Test+at+Hand+to+Prove+the+Saints&amp;rft.btitle=Journal+of+Discourses+Delivered+by+President+Brigham+Young%2C+His+Two+Counsellors%2C+and+the+Twelve+Apostles%2C+and+Others&amp;rft.place=Liverpool&amp;rft.pages=138-45&amp;rft.pub=S.W.+Richards&amp;rft.date=1856-12-21&amp;rft.aulast=Kimball&amp;rft.aufirst=Heber+C.&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fen.wikisource.org%2Fwiki%2FJournal_of_Discourses%2FVolume_4%2FReformation%25E2%2580%2594A_Test_at_Hand_to_Prove_the_Saints%3Foldid%3D462005&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AMormon+Reformation" class="Z3988"></span>.</li>
<li><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><cite id="CITEREFWoodruff1856" class="citation cs2">Woodruff, Wilford (October 6, 1856), <a class="external text" href="https://en.wikisource.org/wiki/Journal_of_Discourses/Volume_4/The_Facilities_Afforded_by_the_Hand-cart_Movement_for_the_Gathering_of_Israel%2C_etc.?oldid=461922">"The Facilities Afforded by the Hand-cart Movement for the Gathering of Israel—The Saints Specially Opposed by the Devil in Any New Enterprise—Reformation"</a>, in Watt, G. D. (ed.), <i>Journal of Discourses Delivered by President Brigham Young, His Two Counsellors, and the Twelve Apostles, and Others</i>, vol.&#160;4, Liverpool: S. W. Richards, pp.&#160;94–100</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.atitle=The+Facilities+Afforded+by+the+Hand-cart+Movement+for+the+Gathering+of+Israel%E2%80%94The+Saints+Specially+Opposed+by+the+Devil+in+Any+New+Enterprise%E2%80%94Reformation&amp;rft.btitle=Journal+of+Discourses+Delivered+by+President+Brigham+Young%2C+His+Two+Counsellors%2C+and+the+Twelve+Apostles%2C+and+Others&amp;rft.place=Liverpool&amp;rft.pages=94-100&amp;rft.pub=S.+W.+Richards&amp;rft.date=1856-10-06&amp;rft.aulast=Woodruff&amp;rft.aufirst=Wilford&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fen.wikisource.org%2Fwiki%2FJournal_of_Discourses%2FVolume_4%2FThe_Facilities_Afforded_by_the_Hand-cart_Movement_for_the_Gathering_of_Israel%252C_etc.%3Foldid%3D461922&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AMormon+Reformation" class="Z3988"></span>.</li>
<li><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><cite id="CITEREFYoung1856" class="citation cs2">Young, Brigham (November 2, 1856), <a class="external text" href="https://en.wikisource.org/wiki/Journal_of_Discourses/Volume_4/Reformation_Necessary_Among_the_Saints%E2%80%94Infidel_Philosophy?oldid=461609">"Reformation Necessary Among The Saints—Infidel Philosophy"</a>, in Watt, G. D. (ed.), <i>Journal of Discourses Delivered by President Brigham Young, His Two Counsellors, and the Twelve Apostles, and Others</i>, vol.&#160;4, Liverpool: S. W. Richards, pp.&#160;58–63</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.atitle=Reformation+Necessary+Among+The+Saints%E2%80%94Infidel+Philosophy&amp;rft.btitle=Journal+of+Discourses+Delivered+by+President+Brigham+Young%2C+His+Two+Counsellors%2C+and+the+Twelve+Apostles%2C+and+Others&amp;rft.place=Liverpool&amp;rft.pages=58-63&amp;rft.pub=S.+W.+Richards&amp;rft.date=1856-11-02&amp;rft.aulast=Young&amp;rft.aufirst=Brigham&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fen.wikisource.org%2Fwiki%2FJournal_of_Discourses%2FVolume_4%2FReformation_Necessary_Among_the_Saints%25E2%2580%2594Infidel_Philosophy%3Foldid%3D461609&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AMormon+Reformation" class="Z3988"></span>.</li></ul>
<h2><span class="mw-headline" id="External_links">External links</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Mormon_Reformation&amp;action=edit&amp;section=9" title="Edit section: External links"><span>edit</span></a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h2>
<ul><li><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://cdm15999.contentdm.oclc.org/cdm/ref/collection/p15999coll24/id/32323">Questions to be asked the Latter-day Saints</a> during the Reformation, MSS SC 292, <a href="/wiki/L._Tom_Perry_Special_Collections" class="mw-redirect" title="L. Tom Perry Special Collections">L. Tom Perry Special Collections</a>, <a href="/wiki/Harold_B._Lee_Library" title="Harold B. Lee Library">Harold B. Lee Library</a>, <a href="/wiki/Brigham_Young_University" title="Brigham Young University">Brigham Young University</a></li></ul>
